            <title><![CDATA[New Call Of Duty Bundle Lets You Fry Your Enemy's Face In Bacon Grease]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/new-call-of-duty-bundle-lets-you-fry-your-enemys-face-in-bacon-grease/1100-6531005/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
